🛡️ SafeHer – Women’s Security & Safety Solutions

SafeHer is a modern, responsive landing page designed for a women-focused safety application. It highlights key safety features such as live location sharing, SOS alerts, community support, and smart notifications — all wrapped in a clean and user-friendly interface.

This project is built using HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript with a strong focus on UI/UX and responsiveness.
🌟 Features
🎨 Modern gradient-based UI design
📱 Fully responsive layout (mobile-friendly)
🚨 SOS emergency badge animation
📍 Live location sharing feature showcase
🔔 Smart alert & notification section\
⭐ Testimonials section
📊 Statistics display section\
📜 Smooth scrolling navigation
✨ Scroll-triggered animations
📱 Mobile menu toggle
🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3 (Flexbox + Grid + Animations)
JavaScript (ES6)
Font Awesome Icons (CDN)
